- Okay. thank you. Martha.

496
00:25:31.458 --> 00:25:32.874
This is a church function. Vera.

497
00:25:32.875 --> 00:25:34.789
It's at a church.
It's with me. It's official.

498
00:25:34.790 --> 00:25:36.164
- Um...
- Or "holy".

499
00:25:36.165 --> 00:25:38.457
