- Yeah.

502
00:25:41.500 --> 00:25:42.457
[Nat] Oh. wow.

503
00:25:42.458 --> 00:25:44.875
Yeah. sorry. Father.
I don't want to piss him off.

504
00:25:45.583 --> 00:25:47.082
Nice try. guy.

505
00:25:47.083 --> 00:25:48.124
Thanks. Doc.

506
00:25:48.125 --> 00:25:50.624
