558
00:28:47.500 --> 00:28:48.333
Really?

559
00:28:49.500 --> 00:28:52.333
[Jud] <i>I mean.
it's mostly symbolic. but yeah.</i>

560
00:28:53.125 --> 00:28:55.124
And Simone. I'm sorry. Monsignor.

561
00:28:55.125 --> 00:28:57.414
but I'm afraid
