it makes her feel betrayed again.

569
00:29:16.208 --> 00:29:17.874
God help me. Anything else?

570
00:29:17.875 --> 00:29:20.207
Yeah. why not? Cy Draven.

571
00:29:20.208 --> 00:29:23.664
<i>Doesn't this new YouTube stuff
