582
00:29:52.040 --> 00:29:54.250
Is that what we're supposed to do?

583
00:29:59.250 --> 00:30:00.664
- [grunts]
- [groans]

584
00:30:00.665 --> 00:30:02.707
- [crows cawing. fluttering]
- [coughing]

585
00:30:02.708 --> 00:30:06.457
Right now. you're angry. You should be.

586
00:30:06.458 --> 00:30:08.874
It'd be dangerous if you weren't.
I'd see you're helpless.

587
00:30:08.875 --> 00:30:11.000
