630
00:32:48.750 --> 00:32:51.582
The world's a wolf. You devil.

631
00:32:51.583 --> 00:32:53.290
You devil wolf.

632
00:32:53.790 --> 00:32:55.208
You're a devil wolf.

633
00:32:56.000 --> 00:32:57.208
Shit.

634
