642
00:33:27.833 --> 00:33:28.875
Oh. shit.

643
00:33:30.333 --> 00:33:32.458
[Jud] <i>And that brings us to Good Friday.</i>

644
00:33:34.625 --> 00:33:35.999
<i>Here we go.</i>

645
00:33:36.000 --> 00:33:38.208
