654
00:34:06.708 --> 00:34:09.039
<i>He would duck into
the small storage closet</i>

655
00:34:09.041 --> 00:34:12.000
<i>just to the side of the sanctuary
so he'd be out of sight.</i>

656
00:34:13.208 --> 00:34:16.289
