752
00:40:52.791 --> 00:40:54.625
How does it make me feel?

753
00:40:59.208 --> 00:41:00.039
Truthfully?

754
00:41:00.041 --> 00:41:01.208
Sure.

755
00:41:03.541 --> 00:41:05.375
