1046
00:56:13.333 --> 00:56:15.083
False priest!

1047
00:56:17.958 --> 00:56:19.541
- Sorry.
- [gasps softly]

1048
00:56:20.375 --> 00:56:22.539
But. yeah.
if finding the facts with that detective

1049
00:56:22.541 --> 00:56:24.791
