1134
01:00:34.833 --> 01:00:37.623
The story of the Reverend Wicks' murder.

1135
01:00:37.625 --> 01:00:38.789
Monsignor Wicks.

1136
01:00:38.791 --> 01:00:40.706
Monsignor JalapeÃ±o. I don't care.

